Y/: yadm helper scripts
This is a set of yadm helper scripts.

brief documents (may not accurate, please refer to actual scripts):
SCRIPTS
    Y/ar <config> <operation> [args... ]: perform path/exclude list operations
        OPERATIONS
            ap/add-path
            ae/add-exclude
            rp/rm-path
            re/rm-exclude
            ep/edit-path
            ee/edit-exclude
    Y/save <config> [commit_message]: save files (yadm add and commit)
    Y/sort <config>: sort and uniq path and exclude lists
FILES
    Y/template: executable, copy one to create a new script
    Y/COMMON: common parts of the scripts, non-executable
    Y/CONFIG/<config>/: config directory
        CONTENT
            PATH: path(include) list
            EXCLUDE: exclude(ignore) list
            yadm/: yadm config dir, refer to yadm(1):FILES
    Y/DATA/<config>/: yadm data dir, refer to yadm(1):FILES
        CONTENT
            repo.git/: yadm git repo
            ...

AS THE `LICENSE` SYMLINK, THEY'RE DISTRIBUTED
UNDER THE SAME LICENSE OF THE WHOLE REPO
